### Create Direct Consent (Tablet Flow)
POST http://localhost:8085/admin/consents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "customer-uuid-123",
  "policies": [
    { "slug": "privacy-policy" },
    { "slug": "marketing-consent" }
  ]
}

### Create Consent with Specific Version
POST http://localhost:8085/admin/consents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "customer-uuid-456",
  "policies": [
    { "slug": "privacy-policy", "version": "1.0.0" }
  ]
}

### Get All Consents for a Subject
GET http://localhost:8085/admin/consents?subject=customer-uuid-123

### Get Specific Policy Consent for Subject
GET http://localhost:8085/admin/consents?subject=customer-uuid-123&policy=privacy-policy

